snippet.title: Wordle Peaks - A New Wordle Variant!
snippet.description:
How to Play Wordle Peaks | Daily Wordle Peaks Puzzle 55 Answer Word for 20th April, 2022

Wordle Peaks is a word puzzle game based on the theme of Wordle Game. So, this Wordle Peaks is kind of a variant of the Wordle Game. Wordle Peaks is like - Where in the Alphabet is the answer?

This video is all about What is Wordle Peaks, How to Play Wordle Peaks, the Rules of Wordle Peaks, The meaning of Color Codes in Wordle Peaks, The difference between the Meaning of the Color Codes of Wordle and Wordle Peaks and lastly Gameplay Walkthrough of Wordle Peaks.

in this video, I have solved the Daily Wordle Peaks Puzzle 55 or Wordle Peaks 55 for 20 April or April 20 or 20th April or April 20th 2022 (04/20/2022) or (4/20/22).

Wordle Peaks Game Link: https://vegeta897.github.io/wordle-peaks/

How to play?
Guess the 5-letter word in 6 tries! After entering a guess the tiles be changed to some color code; likewise Wordle! but the color codes in Wordle Peaks have different meaning  then that of color codes of Wordle. Here, After each guess, the tiles show whether your letters occur correctly (green) or higher (orange) or lower (blue) in the alphabet compared to the correct letters. Higher means closer to A, lower means closer to Z. This game shows the range of possible letters for each slot of letters after giving the first try.
